front.title: •4-LOM
front.gametext: Total power at same site is +1 for each of your alien/droid pairs present. Once during each battle, if present with Zuckuss, may use 1 Force to search any Used Pile and move 1 character there to the Lost Pile. May initiate battle and be battled.
front.lore: Information Broker. Thief. Overrode and reprogrammed its own selfgoverning software. Convinced Jabba the Hut to upgrade its armor and weaponry. Became a bounty hunter.

rulings: A character may not be used in multiple pairs.
